Remove religion for the set of facts and you have ZERO basis for conflict.  <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>NONE.</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->  No people are going to fear other similar people moving into their towns.  They may be pissed you are giving groceries away at your stores and skip out on the money you owe for establishing that store, but they won't burn your neighbors house for your larcenous fraud.  Racism can't be claimed.  Sexism can't be claimed.  Gerontism can't be claimed.  It all hinges on the religion.  The xian faith is based on a war god.  You try and equate horrible crimes as acts of war and it is only a sham to assuage some associative guilt you may feel for being in that same group.  There was no war.  They weren't defending themselves.  they were not invaded or attacked.  They just murdered.  <br>
